{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnlinestylelayer\/linecap"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"lineCap","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"lineCap","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"lineCap","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNLineStyleLayer(py)lineCap"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer\/lineCap"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The display of line endings.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"lineCap"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is an expression that evaluates to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"butt"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Set this property to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" to reset it to the default value.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Constant "},{"code":"MLNLineCap","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any of the following constant string values:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"butt","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": A cap with a squared-off end which is drawn to the exact endpoint"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the line."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"round","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": A cap with a rounded end which is drawn beyond the endpoint of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"line at a radius of one-half of the line’s width and centered on the endpoint"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the line."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"square","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": A cap with a squared-off end which is drawn beyond the endpoint"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the line at a distance of one-half of the line’s width."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Predefined functions, including mathematical and string operators"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Conditional expressions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Variable assignments and references to assigned variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Step functions applied to the "},{"code":"$zoomLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" variable"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not support applying interpolation functions to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"$zoomLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" variable or applying interpolation or step functions to feature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attributes."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNLineStyleLayer/lineCap":{"fragments":[{"text":"lineCap","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnlinestylelayer